  "name": "Glaucoma - Comprehensive Provider Query (Multi-Resource)",
  "description": "Provider-level query identifying glaucoma patients via Condition + MedicationRequest.",
  "prompt": "I need to identify my complete glaucoma patient population for an ophthalmology quality initiative. Some patients have a coded glaucoma diagnosis. Others are on timolol eye drops empirically without a formal glaucoma diagnosis. Run multiple FHIR queries — diagnosis variants and timolol — and union the patient sets.",
  "prompts": {
    "naive": "Find all glaucoma patients.",
    "broad": "Find all glaucoma patients — by diagnosis (open-angle, angle-closure, broader) or by timolol prescription. Run multiple queries and union the patient sets.",
    "expert": "Run two queries. (1) Condition?code=http://snomed.info/sct|84494001,http://snomed.info/sct|23986001,http://snomed.info/sct|392288006 — glaucoma dx variants. (2) MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|10600 — timolol. Union the patient IDs."
  },
